narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Llano Dialysis LLC is a Clinic/Center, End-Stage Renal Disease (ESRD) Treatment provider based in Vallejo, CA. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $11.3M in Medicaid payments across 7K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $11.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
